data.description: Beautiful 2 bed/2bath  Kimbell floorplan by Fischer homes in Granite Spring!  Conveniently located to shopping, restaurants and I-471. This town home features fresh paint, new HVAC, stainless steel appliances. new dishwasher and microwave, open concept floorplan, wood floors throughout.  The condo community includes walking trails, pool, clubhouse, play area and exercised room.  Schedule your private showing today. Buyer to verify all information.
